      • computeDiffInDays

        static int computeDiffInDays(Calendar cal1,
                    Calendar cal2)
        This function tries to emulate the behaviour of DateDiff function from VBA. See a table of its results here.
        Parameters:
        cal1 - calendar, representing the first instant
        cal2 - calendar, representing the second instant
        Returns:
        difference in days with respect to the behaviour of DateDiff function
